Enum TestInstance.Lifecycle

    TestInstance

    public static enum TestInstance.Lifecycle
extends java.lang.Enum<TestInstance.Lifecycle>
    Enumeration of test instance lifecycle modes.
    See Also:
    PER_METHOD, PER_CLASS

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      PER_CLASS
      When using this mode, a new test instance will be created once per test class.
      PER_METHOD
      When using this mode, a new test instance will be created for each test method or test factory method.

      • PER_METHOD

        public static final TestInstance.Lifecycle PER_METHOD
        When using this mode, a new test instance will be created for each test method or test factory method.

        This mode is analogous to the behavior found in JUnit versions 1 through 4.
